<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 18:19:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京就乌克兰袭击向西方发出核警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-says-russia-reserves-right-use-nuclear-weapons-if-attacked-2024-09-25/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周三警告西方，如果俄罗斯遭到常规导弹袭击，俄罗斯可能会使用核武器，并且莫斯科将把任何在核国家支持下对其进行的攻击视为联合攻击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putin-says-russia-reserves-right-use-nuclear-weapons-if-attacked-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>被禁止的检查员不太可能返回伊朗。国际原子能机构负责人表示：“船已经起航”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/return-barred-inspectors-iran-unlikely-iaea-chief-says-ship-has-sailed-2024-09-25/</link><description>联合国核监督机构一直在敦促伊朗取消对几名铀浓缩检查员进入伊朗核设施的禁令，但国际原子能机构负责人告诉路透社，成功似乎不太可能。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 15:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/return-barred-inspectors-iran-unlikely-iaea-chief-says-ship-has-sailed-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基瞄准中国、巴西推动乌克兰和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiy-takes-aim-china-brazil-push-peace-ukraine-2024-09-25/</link><description>泽伦斯基说：“你不会以牺牲乌克兰为代价来增强你的权力。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 15:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiy-takes-aim-china-brazil-push-peace-ukraine-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示，美国对俄罗斯在中国秘密战争无人机项目的报道感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-concerned-by-report-russia-secret-war-drones-project-china-white-house-says-2024-09-25/</link><description>白宫发言人周三表示，美国对俄罗斯在中国开展秘密战争无人机项目的报道深感担忧，该项目似乎是一家中国公司向一家美国制裁的俄罗斯公司提供致命援助的例子。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 13:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-concerned-by-report-russia-secret-war-drones-project-china-white-house-says-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>印度制造业激励措施在减少中国进口的努力中取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-manufacturing-incentives-progress-amid-efforts-cut-china-imports-2024-09-25/</link><description>一位政府官员周三表示，自 2020 年推出生产挂钩计划以来，印度为促进国内制造业而采取的现金激励措施已吸引了超过 170 亿美元的投资，同时努力减少从中国的进口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 13:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-manufacturing-incentives-progress-amid-efforts-cut-china-imports-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>意大利警方称破获利用中国资金掮客的贩毒团伙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/drug-gang-using-chinese-money-brokers-uncovered-italian-police-say-2024-09-25/</link><description>意大利警方周三表示，在对国际贩毒和洗钱活动进行调查后，他们在四个国家逮捕了 61 人，并查获了 6000 万欧元（6710 万美元）的资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/drug-gang-using-chinese-money-brokers-uncovered-italian-police-say-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国国务院发布经济困难时期促进就业指导意见</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-issues-guidelines-promote-employment-2024-09-25/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国务院周三发布了促进高质量充分就业的指导意见，承诺把就业放在经济社会发展的优先位置，促进工资合理增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:10:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-issues-guidelines-promote-employment-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，8月份外国智能手机在华销量下降12.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-127-august-data-show-2024-09-25/</link><description>一家政府下属研究公司周三发布的数据显示，8月份包括苹果公司iPhone在内的外国品牌智能手机在中国的销量同比下降12.7%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-127-august-data-show-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>大阪希望与新教练莫拉托格鲁建立长期合作关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/osaka-eyes-long-term-partnership-with-new-coach-mouratoglou-2024-09-25/</link><description>大坂直美正在寻求重振她的职业生涯。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/osaka-eyes-long-term-partnership-with-new-coach-mouratoglou-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>随着焦点转向英国预算，英镑兑美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/sterling-slips-against-dollar-focus-turns-uk-budget-2024-09-25/</link><description>英镑兑美元周三下跌，从一天前的两年半高点回落，投资者将注意力转向下个月的英国预算以及八天后到期的英国央行利率决定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:20:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/sterling-slips-against-dollar-focus-turns-uk-budget-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国信心动摇，中国信心提振</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-25/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将在联合国大会间隙会见越南领导人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-meet-vietnam-leader-un-assembly-sidelines-2024-09-25/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三与越南总统林涛举行会谈，旨在深化与这个东南亚国家和制造业中心的关系，并对抗其与中国和俄罗斯的关系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-meet-vietnam-leader-un-assembly-sidelines-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>优步与中国自动驾驶科技初创公司宣布合作在阿联酋推出机器人出租车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/uber-chinese-self-driving-tech-startup-announce-partnership-launch-robotaxis-uae-2024-09-25/</link><description>优步科技 (Uber Technologies) 和文远知行文远知行 (WeRide) 周三宣布建立合作伙伴关系，将这家中国自动驾驶技术公司的车辆引入共享出行平台，首先从阿拉伯联合酋长国开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/uber-chinese-self-driving-tech-startup-announce-partnership-launch-robotaxis-uae-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：英特尔消息人士称，俄罗斯在中国有秘密战争无人机项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-has-secret-war-drones-project-china-intel-sources-say-2024-09-25/</link><description>该项目旨在开发和生产用于对乌克兰战争的远程攻击无人机。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 10:08:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-has-secret-war-drones-project-china-intel-sources-say-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国顶尖电子烟公司研究尼古丁替代品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/top-chinese-vape-firms-research-nicotine-alternatives-2024-09-25/</link><description>公司官员表示，中国三大电子烟公司正在研究尼古丁类化学物质，他们认为可以作为电子烟等产品中尼古丁的替代品，但其对健康的影响可能仍需要“数年”的调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:36:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/top-chinese-vape-firms-research-nicotine-alternatives-2024-09-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>